Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: 600 Main is located within a qualified opportunity zone, providing tax advantages to investors. The property is located on a prominent corner, just 1 mile from downtown Nashville and offers easy access to surrounding neighborhoods and major interstates. 600 Main offers easy access to a variety of popular East Nashville restaurants, bars, and music/arts venues.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE is pleased to announce for sale, 600 Main Street, a 9,855 square foot Office/Retail Building in East Nashville. Located on a main thoroughfare, the site is in close proximity and offers easy access to Downtown Nashville, area amenities, and Nashville’s hottest neighborhoods. The property has a WalkScore of 81, which is considered “very walkable” to surrounding amenities.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Minutes from I-65, Historic Downtown Franklin, and Cool Springs Galleria.
Close proximity to restaurants, banks, and retail.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Just twenty miles from Nashville, Franklin has anchored its development in a unique heritage that honors its charming character while progressively becoming a leader in statewide population and job growth. Alongside Franklin’s economic and business development has been the growth of a sought after lifestyle community, providing business owners with a progressive and thriving demographic. Franklin continues to look forward in growing it’s identity as a business hub by actively collaborating with existing businesses to continually identify catalysts for future development. Becoming a member of the business-owning community in Franklin provides the opportunity to become a contributing voice in the broader landscape that ultimately contributes to further growth for all local owners.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: The average office condo will consist of 5,067 square feet and will be offered at an average of $1,729,000. Office condos range from 2,669 square feet for $890,000 to 7,237 square feet for $2,460,000 with a 1,200 SF terrace. Owners will have the benefit of an accommodating 4/1,000 square foot ratio. This will give Owners and guests a surplus of easy access parking to choose from including a 150 space below grade parking garage with elevator access direct to the Owners space.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: 345 Main Street is located in the heart of downtown Franklin. Walk to nearby restaurants, enjoy live entertainment, and shop for local artisan goods in Franklin’s vibrant small business district.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE is pleased to exclusively offer for sale, 345 Main Street., a beautiful, two-story historic office building in the heart of Downtown Franklin. 345 Main Street consists of three suites in total. This includes a first-floor retail space and two separate office suites on the 2nd floor. White Mercantile currently occupies the 1st floor and Red's All Natural Burritos occupies the office suites on the 2nd floor.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
The Property is located in Ridgeway Center, a 204-acre mixed use development at Poplar Avenue & Interstate 240 comprised of over one (1) million square feet of space. 
The East Memphis Submarket is the most desirable office market for high profile tenants with its convenient access to major transit corridors, high-income residential neighborhoods and numerous upscale amenities.  The submarket maintains the largest concentration of Class A product in the market at 3.3M SF as well historically low vacancy and highest rental rates compared to Memphis MSA.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE, Inc., as exclusive advisor, is pleased to present the opportunity to acquire 860 Ridge Lake, Memphis, TN, (the “Property”), a 154,558 SF division headquarters facility located within Ridgeway Center, an institutional quality office park along Memphis’s premier office corridor. This investment oﬀers a well-positioned office asset 100%-leased through 2028 to ABB, Inc., the operating entity for ABB, Ltd. (NYSE: ABB, S&P: A-), operations in the United States and Canada.
